export const groupingMap = [
    {
        label: "Abis Switch Side",
        color: "abis",
        colspan: 0,
        columns: [

            {
                data: "archived",

                manually: true,
                width: 130
            },
            {
                data: "decommissionDate",

                manually: true,
                width: 100
